summary:
I am an experienced iOS developer with over a decade of experience, having started in 2011. Throughout my career, I have worked in various areas of the industry, ranging from startups in their early stages to established and renowned companies. My diverse range of experiences has given me a unique perspective on different industries and has helped me to develop a highly adaptable and versatile skillset. I strongly believe in the value of working closely with designers to ensure that our collective efforts lead to a maximized user experience. 
Additionally, I hold passports from both Italy and Brazil, allowing me to work seamlessly in multiple locations and cultures.
